::Bazooka::

    Bazooka followed the signal to an open feild. He did not see Magmatron 
anywhere. "This is to be expected." He went on his way to the real location 
after reciving a silent transmission from Magmatron.
    He reached the base. Inside he found a new impressive Magmatron. Looking 
around he saw all the computer equpment. On one screen he saw a digram of a 
key, he didn't know what it was for. 
    "Commander Magmatron may I tour the base?" Bazooka asked. Magmatron let 
him. On his way through he found a huge cash of weapons. Some were bigger 
than his hands, his hands are pretty big.
    "This is enough to kill even Optimus." Bazooka said. In another room he 
found a lab. Magmatron came up behind him. "What is this for?" Bazooka asked.
    "Just in case any of my troops will be destroyed when the Ark is. It will 
alter their forms just slightly so that they have no Decpticon or Autobot 
traces left in them. That way they will not be destroyed." Magmatron replied.
